Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.33,0:47:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.49,0:47:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.83,0:47:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's a good question.
