Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.48,0:47:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.66,0:47:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.74,0:47:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.80,0:47:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.98,0:47:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.04,0:47:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.22,0:47:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.24,0:47:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.30,0:47:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.36,0:47:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.44,0:47:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.46,0:47:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.54,0:47:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.58,0:47:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,as as a teacher would you call yourself successful? Oh successful well I'm happy
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.28,0:48:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm successful and then I'm happy that I have a chance to speak spontaneously in
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.87,0:48:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a forthright and honest way that is not stilted and stylized which which often
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.86,0:48:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,turns people off on what they consider spiritual but many people are turned off
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.76,0:48:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,by anything they hear is spiritual because they expect all this holy roller
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.28,0:48:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,stylized not too realistic kind of expression of prayerfulness and
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.78,0:48:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,holiness and you know you might say excess being spontaneously joyful and
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.32,0:48:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,being spontaneously the reality of that which I am I consider that spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.14,0:48:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,give me a kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.95,0:49:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think of that it just was I wanted to like say thank you God that you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.65,0:49:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,brought the thought to my mind which I meant to express and I'm very happy to
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.53,0:49:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to do that I mean I'm only have this body for a while and I want to use
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.67,0:49:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it to express my understanding of spirituality because it might be a value
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.89,0:49:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.30,0:49:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody served it's value to me but it might be helpful to somebody else so as
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.57,0:49:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a more stilted view of it so my view of spirituality is probably less stilted
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.00,0:49:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,than some people who tend to be sanctimonious you know you might say
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.95,0:49:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,sanctimonious and think that being spiritual is an awkward and difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.26,0:49:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,way of life sackcloth and ashes kind of deal mm-hmm not there's any wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.58,0:50:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But as a spiritual teacher you know we've as us we've tried to convey every question
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.94,0:50:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that maybe the spiritual person would ask so that's why we're doing these talks
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.96,0:50:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think yes we're trying and we're trying to record it and so that if questions arise
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.74,0:50:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.06,0:50:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,they will be answered
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.10,0:50:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're trying to expand
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.62,0:50:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.46,0:50:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of what's meant by the term
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.66,0:50:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.36,0:50:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or success
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.40,0:50:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people really dwell on success
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.46,0:50:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not successful unless
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.96,0:50:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a million dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.72,0:50:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in the bank
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.26,0:50:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,or I'm not successful unless I get that job
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.24,0:50:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,or I'm not successful unless I have that car
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.64,0:50:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so they have their own definitions
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.96,0:50:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and those are all goals
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.70,0:50:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that people set for each other
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.92,0:51:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but you brought up the fact that they need to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.60,0:51:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,balance that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.86,0:51:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,between their spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.52,0:51:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,life and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.38,0:51:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the monetary
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.26,0:51:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,success of life
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.82,0:51:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,they will be more successful if they balance it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.12,0:51:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,than if they just
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.34,0:51:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,focus on success itself
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.92,0:51:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because just
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.14,0:51:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,worldly success
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.34,0:51:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,as a 100% focus
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.74,0:51:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to turn people off
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.42,0:51:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to a certain extent
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.50,0:51:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you watch them on television
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.84,0:51:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you can tell
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.44,0:51:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you can tell
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.48,0:51:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you can tell
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.50,0:51:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,they're all about me, me, me, me, me
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.10,0:51:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and that tends to turn you off after a while
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.58,0:51:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's one
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.92,0:51:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,reason we like comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.34,0:51:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is because comedians tend to make light of their
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.24,0:51:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of the human limitations
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.82,0:51:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to make humorous
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.70,0:51:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what would otherwise be painful
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.64,0:51:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,serves a spiritual purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.70,0:51:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I also thought humorous
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.78,0:51:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,tended for a long life
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.70,0:51:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and the contribution of humor
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.54,0:52:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to life
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.25,0:52:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because they help us to laugh at ourself
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.43,0:52:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,at what otherwise
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.79,0:52:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,might be quite painful
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.04,0:52:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and embarrassing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.96,0:52:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we can take ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.04,0:52:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack Benny can take us
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.46,0:52:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we can take ourselves lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.60,0:52:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that dates me
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.84,0:52:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jack Benny is he
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.20,0:52:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.04,0:52:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
