Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.92,0:52:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.52,0:52:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,oh no
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.38,0:52:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway Jack Benny
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.66,0:52:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,symbolizes the ultimate of the
