Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.20,0:52:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,oh
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.35,0:52:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.49,0:52:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so success
