Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.03,0:52:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,no?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.53,0:52:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so success is
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.81,0:52:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.63,0:52:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is something that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.37,0:52:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,we all work for
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.41,0:52:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we do it with balance
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.19,0:52:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and we achieve our goals
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.87,0:52:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,um
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.87,0:52:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,does God's will
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.29,0:52:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,have anything to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.46,0:52:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,well I think God's will is like the weather
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.74,0:53:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it influences everything
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.36,0:53:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,ok
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.12,0:53:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,um both directly and indirectly
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.78,0:53:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,um both directly and indirectly
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.08,0:53:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think God's will is that we as human beings fulfill our potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.67,0:53:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and because the human spirit goes on from one physical lifetime on to another
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.69,0:53:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,it grows over a number of physical lifetimes you know
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.91,0:53:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and we call it karma
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.11,0:53:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it needs four or five physical lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.67,0:53:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to fulfill a spiritual goal
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.97,0:53:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.97,0:53:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.97,0:53:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.35,0:53:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel happy that we went to church
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.05,0:53:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel happy that we went to church
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.88,0:53:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.88,0:53:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,this week
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.88,0:53:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.36,0:53:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that's an occasion that I
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.36,0:53:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.36,0:53:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in previous years did we go for Ash Wednesday?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.36,0:53:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.36,0:53:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.36,0:53:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.36,0:53:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.42,0:53:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,oh ok
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.84,0:53:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,uh
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.84,0:53:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.99,0:53:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's both symbolic on a very deep level
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.11,0:54:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and on another level it's not even necessary you might say
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.09,0:54:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.82,0:54:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so I say to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.22,0:54:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,now why in the world do we get up early and go to Ash Wednesday?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.06,0:54:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to go to church today you see what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.60,0:54:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.88,0:54:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,every year the answer is different
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.88,0:54:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,right
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.88,0:54:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.88,0:54:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're in a different mood a different decade of life
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.88,0:54:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and the older you get the more you realize that you better be going to church every Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.36,0:54:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.36,0:54:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.00,0:54:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the closer you get to being a hundred the more you know it's important you go to church every Sunday
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.00,0:54:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.00,0:54:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.00,0:54:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.19,0:54:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,do you feel like we've covered everything you want to say on success?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.73,0:54:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,oh well I could talk all day long about success
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.11,0:54:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you know and as a psychiatrist I uh
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.42,0:54:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that often became important
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.42,0:55:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,whether when it's successful in their marriage as a father as a parent
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.46,0:55:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in their children in their physical expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.46,0:55:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,financial self expectation is so important
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.81,0:55:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,uh yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.16,0:55:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and so in defining success
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.24,0:55:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope as we speak today that I'm being as fluent
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.20,0:55:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,as possible in fulfilling your questions
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.96,0:55:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so that would be to me success
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.30,0:55:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,then if on the way home from here I suddenly think I should have answered it better in a certain area
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.40,0:55:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,then I will consider myself successful if I stopped feeling guilty that I didn't answer it better
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.86,0:55:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,uh huh
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.70,0:55:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we're going to wrap it up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.12,0:55:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wrap it up, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.10,0:55:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So is there anything else you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.99,0:56:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I feel myself to be successful that I have you in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.60,0:56:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the two of us are sitting here and the camera is focused on us
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.67,0:56:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore that more than just you and myself will be hearing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.80,0:56:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I consider that the fulfillment of success,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.72,0:56:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that your life is contributing to the life of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.70,0:56:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So to me, success is your life is contributing to the life of others
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.20,0:56:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,if nothing else but stirring up the question in their own mind
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.95,0:56:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,after they listen to this and they say,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.31,0:56:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,well, what do I consider success?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.99,0:56:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it brings up the question in their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.35,0:56:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So we all grow through the questions that we ask ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.94,0:56:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So to the degree that we're helping other people to grow,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.83,0:56:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel my life is a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.62,0:56:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thank you for making my life a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.78,0:56:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thank you for being in mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.32,0:56:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.66,0:57:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll be a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.64,0:57:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
